long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Add a dash of cute Halloween magic to your new tab with Halloween Cute Anime! This Chrome extension brings festive anime style to your browser.

The Halloween Cute Anime live wallpaper extension showcases an adorable anime character in a Halloween setting, perfect for fans of both kawaii and spooky aesthetics. With a minimalist layout, it enhances your browsing with essential tools.

Quickly browse with the Google search bar, access favorite sites with customizable shortcuts, and stay on track with a clock-date display.

Key Features:

Live Wallpaper featuring a cute anime Halloween theme
Google Search Bar for fast and easy browsing
Customizable site shortcuts for favorite websites
Clock-Date display for real-time updates

Enjoy Halloween with a kawaii twist! Visit Gameograf.com for more anime-inspired themes to personalize your tabs.
